      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Student CRM Agent for Coaching Owner\n\nBefore using:\n1. Create a Google Sheet named Coaching Student CRM.\n2. Create tab: Students.\n3. Add columns: Student_ID, Student_Name, Parent_Name, Phone, Email, City, Class_Grade, Course_Interest, Exam_Target, Lead_Source, Lead_Status, Demo_Status, Demo_Date, Follow_Up_Date, Batch_Assigned, Fee_Status, Amount_Pending, Last_Contacted, Next_Action, Notes, Created_At, Updated_At.\n4. Replace PASTE_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID_HERE in both Google Sheets tools.\n5. Select your Google Sheets credential.",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 920
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -80,
        -240
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "62934f0f-73b1-46a9-9ff3-7dd65fa5e399",
